{"word":"Servant","slug":"servant","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Servant</b> Bond servant:<br/> - Laws of Moses concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=21&verse=11'>Exo 21:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=21&verse=21'>Exo 21:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=21&verse=27'>Exo 21:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=21&verse=32'>Exo 21:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=19&verse=22'>Lev 19:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=25&verse=6'>Lev 25:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=25&verse=10'>Lev 25:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=25&verse=55'>Lev 25:55</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=15&verse=12'>Deu 15:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=15&verse=14'>Deu 15:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=15&verse=18'>Deu 15:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=24&verse=7'>Deu 24:7</a> <br/> - Manstealing forbidden<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=21&verse=14'>Deu 21:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=24&verse=7'>Deu 24:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=1&verse=10'>1Ti 1:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=18&verse=13'>Rev 18:13</a> <br/> - Fugitive, not to be returned to master<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=23&verse=16'>Deu 23:16</a> <br/> - David erroneously supposed to be a fugitive slave<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=25&verse=10'>1Sa 25:10</a> <br/> - Instances of fugitive, Hagar, commanded by an angel to return to her mistress<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=16&verse=9'>Gen 16:9<